00:18.275 --> 00:19.541
Well, that will interesting.

00:19.543 --> 00:21.309
You... You're the one
that wrote that article

00:21.311 --> 00:23.712
- about Dr. George Hodel?
- George Hodel? Yes.

00:23.714 --> 00:25.547
