better than this garbage, Peter.

02:54.564 --> 02:55.897
It's gonna blow your hair back.

02:55.899 --> 02:57.499
I got an anonymous phone call
last night.

02:57.501 --> 02:59.801
You'll never guess
who it's about.

02:59.803 --> 03:01.002
Who?

03:01.004 --> 03:02.837
Dr. George Hodel.

03:02.839 --> 03:05.440
Nuts.

03:05.442 --> 03:07.742
- No, it's Dr. George Hodel.
- Ah shit, Jay, that...

03:07.744 --> 03:09.644
I am telling you,
I got a feeling...

03:09.646 --> 03:11.279
- You know...
- ...something is up.

03:11.281 --> 03:13.048
This call means something.

03:13.050 --> 03:14.516
There's a crack.

03:14.518 --> 03:18.053
Okay Jay, first of all,
that trial was 10 lifetimes ago.

03:18.055 --> 03:19.454
And second,
you already tried this.

03:19.456 --> 03:21.756
- He walked. End of story.
- Okay, but what if the...

03:21.758 --> 03:23.391
What if the phone call
has new information?

03:23.393 --> 03:25.126
