with the truth, Peter.

03:30.000 --> 03:32.734
Because this... this...
It <i> is</i> the truth.

03:32.736 --> 03:35.136
- I know it's the truth.
- Oh, y... oh, you know it?

03:35.138 --> 03:36.738
Okay, but Hodel's daughter,
Tamar...

03:36.740 --> 03:37.839
Is that her name?

03:37.841 --> 03:40.408
She took it back, Jay,
in the end. Am I right?

03:40.410 --> 03:41.776
That's what <i> they</i> said.
Then I couldn't find her.

03:41.778 --> 03:43.712
They shipped her off to a convent.
Yeah.

03:43.714 --> 03:45.880
Mm. What if this phone
call was Tamar Hodel?

03:45.882 --> 03:48.416
And what would she say?
We got to find out.

03:48.418 --> 03:51.219
I am not jumping in
a bag of snakes with you, Jay.

03:51.221 --> 03:53.922
I am not doing it.
You ain't a kid anymore, Jay.

03:53.924 --> 03:56.858
You know that stunt you pulled?
You didn't just screw yourself.

03:56.860 --> 03:59.060
You know that? Decent guys
got shit-canned because of that.

03:59.062 --> 04:00.295
Of course...
Of course I know that!

04:00.297 --> 04:01.796
Joe Kline
drank himself to death.

04:01.798 --> 04:03.298
- God, of course I...
- Are you friggin' kidding me?

04:03.300 --> 04:04.766
